# JHE OW polling pipeline crontab — read by supercronic in the jhe_cron sidecar.
#
# Runs once per 24 hours at 06:00 UTC. Operators can change the hour by editing
# this file (it is tracked in the repo and rebuilt into the jhe_cron sidecar
# image). The 24h cadence is the polling interval — the management command
# does NOT do a per-patient interval check. See spec D3.
#
# The command no-ops automatically if ow.ingest_mode != "polling", so this
# crontab can keep firing after the operator flips to webhook mode in Q2 2026.
0 6 * * * cd /app && python manage.py ow_poll
